name: Space Science Precinct and the Advanced Instrumentation and Technology Centre (AITC)
details:
Partners in the AITC include EOS Space Systems, Lockheed Martin, NASA Ames Research Centre, Japan's National Institute of Information and Communications, the German Aerospace Centre, Optus, University of New South Wales, CSIRO and the Royal Melbourne Institute of Technology.
Other partners in the precinct include: Space Environment Research Centre CRC, and the ANU Research School of Astronomy and Astrophysics.
